        {
            "id": 6020809,
            "title": "盤中速報 - Applovin Corp - Class A(APP-US)大跌5.17%，報363.59美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Applovin Corp - Class A(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:APP:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/APP\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">APP-US</a>)截至台北時間12日23:09股價下跌19.84美元，報363.59美元，跌幅5.17%，成交量1,928,598（股），盤中最高價384.10美元、最低價362.86美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.07%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.31%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.3%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.47%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>Applovin Corp - Class A(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:APP:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/APP\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">APP-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-7.94%</li> <li>近 1 月：+16.71%</li> <li>近 3 月：+48.75%</li> <li>近 6 月：+13.37%</li> <li>今年以來：+18.4%</li></ul></section></main>",
